285
00:23:47,930 --> 00:23:51,030
<i>No proteins, no enzymes,</i> <i>no nucleic acid.</i>

286
00:23:51,100 --> 00:23:54,390
Impossible! No organism can maintain life without them!

287
00:23:54,460 --> 00:23:56,560
You mean, no Earth organism.

288
00:23:56,630 --> 00:23:58,810
It must have evolved in a totally different way.

289
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:03,130
You got it. It doesn't come from here.

290
00:24:03,190 --> 00:24:05,910
Without chemical reactions there can't be life,

291
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:08,350
yet it grows, reproduces... <i>Wait!</i>

292
00:24:08,410 --> 00:24:11,350
