Folks at Piedmont was good, decent, normal folks.

345
00:28:51,800 --> 00:28:55,280
The man we found dressed up in his doughboy's uniform, call that normal?

346
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:58,620
Pete Arnold, who worked at the store.

347
00:28:58,680 --> 00:29:01,270
