00:31:12,220 --> 00:31:16,340
- Nothing... so far. - Then you're back where you started.

370
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:19,090
No. Somehow they're all interrelated.

371
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:24,180
I'll have the answer when I know why a 69-year-old Sterno drinker with an ulcer...

372
00:31:24,250 --> 00:31:27,150
