00:33:17,980 --> 00:33:20,880
There haven't been any, sir. The bell didn't ring...

399
00:33:20,950 --> 00:33:23,290
Don't argue, damn it! I've got one in my hand.

400
00:33:25,340 --> 00:33:28,270
Well, well. About time we heard from you.

401
00:33:28,350 --> 00:33:30,390
There has been a communications foul-up. Never mind that now.

402
00:33:30,460 --> 00:33:32,350
Why hasn't that bomb been dropped on Piedmont?

403
00:33:32,410 --> 00:33:36,440
The decision on 7-12 isn't final. It was just postponed 48 hours.

404
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:39,190
By then the disease could spread into a worldwide epidemic.

405
00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:42,900
It's because of rash statements like that the president doesn't trust scientists.

406
00:33:42,970 --> 00:33:45,040
Warn the president it may already be too late.

407
00:33:45,110 --> 00:33:47,700
Stay on his back, Robbie. You've got to make him call a 7-12.

408
00:33:47,770 --> 00:33:50,040
Can you get me another appointment tonight, Grimes?

409
00:33:50,110 --> 00:33:52,820
Now let's all just keep our heads screwed on.

410
00:33:52,890 --> 00:33:56,150
Any thoughts about the Phantom crash?

411
00:33:56,220 --> 00:33:59,030
We sent you a couple messages on it.

412
00:33:59,100 --> 00:34:02,200
A Phantom jet strayed over the cordoned area around Piedmont.

413
00:34:02,270 --> 00:34:04,660
- Any other information? - Well, the pilot said...

414
00:34:04,730 --> 00:34:07,630
that all the rubber on the plane was dissolving.

