00:34:07,710 --> 00:34:09,590
His last communication was pretty weird.

416
00:34:09,660 --> 00:34:12,440
- Like he was crazy? - He was mighty confused, that's for sure.

417
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:16,180
Robbie, it's your job to get the president to activate a 7-12 immediately.

418
00:34:16,250 --> 00:34:19,450
If he doesn't, there's no guarantee anyone west of Piedmont will be alive in the morning.

419
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:22,380
Simmer down, Professor. I'll wake the boss.

420
00:34:22,460 --> 00:34:24,730
But General Sparks says the crash was just a fluke.

421
00:34:24,790 --> 00:34:27,930
Forget the crash, Robbie. Stay on that 7-12 and get back to me.

422
00:34:27,990 --> 00:34:29,850
We'll be working around the clock.

