00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:57,980
Sample in the button and sealed, Charlie. Start the vacuum pump.

433
00:36:06,940 --> 00:36:09,080
Stone, can I see you?

434
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:11,030
I have the results of the growth cultures.

435
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:14,550
No, we can't leave now. We have an Andromeda cell in the E.M.

436
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:17,470
Okay, Charlie, let's put it on the screen.

437
00:36:26,010 --> 00:36:28,910
Let's run it through the computer for contrast expansion.

438
00:36:37,530 --> 00:36:39,950
Stone? What do you think?

439
00:36:42,490 --> 00:36:44,380
<i>It looks like a crystal.</i>

440
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:47,790
- Well, gentlemen, there's our answer. - To what?

441
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:50,520
How Andromeda functions without amino acids.

442
00:36:50,590 --> 00:36:52,560
Crystalline structure. Yes.

443
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:55,000
I've often thought that living matter...

444
00:36:55,070 --> 00:36:57,490
might be based on crystals of some kind.

