449
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:16,760
That's what I wanted to tell you. The growth program...

450
00:37:16,830 --> 00:37:18,930
shows Andromeda can live on anything.

451
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:21,210
Only gas and light affect it.

452
00:37:21,270 --> 00:37:24,590
- You didn't get any no-growth results on the cultures? - None. Look.

453
00:37:28,950 --> 00:37:31,510
The poorest growth occurs in pure oxygen...

454
00:37:31,580 --> 00:37:34,070
<i>incubated under infrared light.</i>

455
00:37:34,140 --> 00:37:36,790
Andromeda grows best in carbon dioxide and hydrogen...

456
00:37:36,860 --> 00:37:38,710
<i>incubated under X rays.</i>

457
00:37:38,780 --> 00:37:40,500
No excretions.

458
00:37:40,570 --> 00:37:43,670
No waste of any kind. You'd expect that.

459
00:37:43,740 --> 00:37:46,640
<i>Andromeda's perfect</i> <i>for existence in outer space.</i>

460
00:37:46,710 --> 00:37:49,580
<i>Consumes everything,</i> <i>wastes nothing.</i>

461
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:56,440
Good Lord. Stone to Delta Five. Put me through to Robertson immediately.

462
00:37:56,510 --> 00:37:58,360
What? God, I hope we're not too late.

463
00:37:58,430 --> 00:38:01,430
- Tell me. - It functions like an atomic reactor.

464
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:03,410
An atomic blast could provide it with enough energy...

465
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:06,070
to grow into a gigantic supercolony. In one day.

466
